column5: Looking for the best place to buy a micro as card lake of the woods lakemaster chip.Any suggestions?Sent from my iPhone using Tapatalk
Assuming this is for a hummingbird, but you can find anything you want on ebay...https://www.ebay.com/itm/Humminbird-...frcectupt=true

I have the Lake Master chip for LOTW and I can tell you that it works really well and worth every penny. With 1 foot contours, you can really see the bottom and find small humps that would be otherwise invisible. I think I bought mine at Scheels. Sorry, mine's not for sale though. Be advised that the northern part of the lake is not in high-def (1 foot contours). At least it wasn't when I bought my card.
The northern part of the lake is very poor. Most of us up here use Navionics.
